---
title: Seared Salmon & Roasted Veggie Couscous with Garlic Yoghurt & Parsley
description: Pearl couscous might just be our favourite grain, providing a fluffy base to any dish! This time its paried with roasted veggies and a garlic-spiked oil to provide loads of flavour, with a blushing pink salmon fillet sitting on top. Grab a fork and dive right in.

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving.*

*We’ve replaced the freekeh in this recipe with pearl couscous
due to local ingredient availability. It’ll be just as delicious, just follow your recipe card!*
